{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl\"><code>Intl</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/@@toStringTag\"><code>Intl[@@toStringTag]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/getCanonicalLocales\"><code>Intl.getCanonicalLocales()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/supportedValuesOf\"><code>Intl.supportedValuesOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Páginas relacionadas:</strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Collator\"><code>Intl.Collator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/ListFormat\"><code>Intl.ListFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/PluralRules\"><code>Intl.PluralRules</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Segmenter\"><code>Intl.Segmenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>Herança:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O objeto&nbsp;<strong><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code></strong> é um construtor de objetos que permitem uma&nbsp;formatação&nbsp;de tempo relativa&nbsp;sensível ao idioma.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/intl-relativetimeformat.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">A fonte deste exemplo interativo está armazenada num repositório no GitHub. Se você quiser contribuir para o projeto de exemplos interativos, por favor clone&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples</a> e nos envie um pull request.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>new Intl.RelativeTimeFormat([<var>locales</var>[, <var>options</var>]])\n</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"locales\"><code>locales</code></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Opcional. Uma string com uma tag da linguagem BCP 47, ou um array dessas strings. Para a forma geral e interpretação do argumento&nbsp;<code>locales</code>&nbsp;, acesse: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#locale_identification_and_negotiation\">Página Intl</a>.</p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code></dt>\n <dd>Opcional. Um objeto com algumas ou todas as seguintes propriedades:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>localeMatcher</code><br>\n   O algoritmo para comparação de local a ser usado. Os valores possíveis são&nbsp;<code>\"lookup\"</code> e <code>\"best fit\"</code>; o padrão é&nbsp;<code>\"best fit\"</code>. Para informações sobre esta opção, veja&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#Locale_negotiation\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code>Intl</code></a>.</li>\n  <li><code>numeric</code><br>\n   O formato de saída da mensagem. Valores possíveis são:\n   <ul>\n    <li><code>\"always\"</code> (padrão, e.g., <code>há 1 dia</code>),</li>\n    <li>ou&nbsp;<code>\"auto\"</code> (e.g., <code>ontem</code>). O valor<code>\"auto\"</code> permite que não seja sempre necessário o uso de valores númericos na saída.</li>\n   </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><code>style</code><br>\n   O comprimento da mensagem internacionalizada. Valores possíveis são:\n   <ul>\n    <li><code>\"long\"</code> (padrão, e.g., <code>in 1 month</code>)</li>\n    <li><code>\"short\"</code> (e.g., <code>in 1 mo.</code>),</li>\n    <li>ou&nbsp;<code>\"narrow\"</code> (e.g., <code>in 1 mo.</code>). O estilo narrow pode ser similar ao short em alguns locais.</li>\n   </ul>\n  </li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"descrição","title":"Descrição","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"intl.relativetimeformat.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Permite a adição de propriedades para todos os objetos.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"intl.relativetimeformat.supportedlocalesof_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat/supportedLocalesOf\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um array contendo os valores disponíveis dentre os que foram passados como parâmetro sem ter de recorrer ao local padrão do ambiente.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instâncias_relativetimeformat","title":"Instâncias <code>RelativeTimeFormat</code>&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"Instâncias RelativeTimeFormat "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades_2","title":"Propriedades","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Instâncias&nbsp;<code>RelativeTimeFormat</code>&nbsp;herdam as seguintes propriedades do seu protótipo:</p>\n\n<p>{{page('/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RelativeTimeFormat/prototype', 'Properties')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos_2","title":"Métodos","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Instâncias <code>RelativeTimeFormat</code>&nbsp; herdam as seguintes propriedades do seu protótipo:</p>\n\n<p>{{page('/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RelativeTimeFormat/prototype', 'Methods')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uso_básico_do_format","title":"Uso básico do&nbsp;<code>format</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O exemplo a seguir mostra como criar um formatador de tempo relativo usando a língua portuguesa.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Crie um formatador de tempo relativo no seu local</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// com os valores padrão sendo passados explicitamente.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rtf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>RelativeTimeFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"pt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">localeMatcher</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"best fit\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// outros valores: \"lookup\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">numeric</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"always\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// outros valores: \"auto\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">style</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"long\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// outros valores: \"short\" ou \"narrow\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Formatação de tempo relativa usando valor negativo (-1).</span>\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; \"há 1 dia\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Formatação de tempo relativa usando valor positivo (1).</span>\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; \"em 1 dia\"</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Uso básico do format"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usando_a_opção_auto","title":"Usando a opção&nbsp;<code>auto</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Se a opção&nbsp;<code>numeric:auto</code>&nbsp;é passada, serão&nbsp;produzidas as strings&nbsp;<code>ontem</code> ou&nbsp;<code>amanhã</code>&nbsp;ao invés de&nbsp;<code>há 1 dia</code> ou&nbsp;<code>em 1 dia</code>. Isso permite que não seja necessário sempre utilizar valores numéricos na saída.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Crie um formatador de tempo relativo no seu local</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// com o valor \"auto\" passado para a propriedade numeric.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rtf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>RelativeTimeFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"pt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">numeric</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"auto\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Formatação de tempo relativa usando valor negativo (-1).</span>\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; \"ontem\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Formatação de tempo relativa usando valor positivo (1).</span>\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; \"amanhã\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Usando a opção auto"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usando_formattoparts","title":"Usando&nbsp;<code>formatToParts</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O exemplo a seguir mostra como criar um formatador de tempo relativo que retorna partes formatadas</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rtf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>RelativeTimeFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">numeric</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"auto\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Formatação de tempo relativa usando a unidade day.</span>\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">formatToParts</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; [{type: \"literal\", value: \"ontem\"}]</span>\n\nrtf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">formatToParts</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"day\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt; [{type: \"literal\", value: \"em \"},</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt;  { type: \"integer\", value: \"100\", unit: \"day\" },</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &gt;  {type: \"literal\", value: \" dias\"]</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Usando formatToParts"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estágio</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.github.io/proposal-intl-relative-time/#sec-intl-relativetimeformat-constructor\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Intl.RelativeTime proposal</a></td>\n   <td>Stage 3</td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2018/10/intl-relativetimeformat\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">The Intl.RelativeTimeFormat API</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Descrição","id":"descrição"},{"text":"Instâncias <code>RelativeTimeFormat</code>&nbsp;","id":"instâncias_relativetimeformat"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"}],"summary":"O objeto Intl.RelativeTimeFormat é um construtor de objetos que permitem uma formatação de tempo relativa sensível ao idioma.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/relativetimeformat","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/relativetimeformat/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl","title":"Intl"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat","title":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat"}],"pageTitle":"Intl.RelativeTimeFormat - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}